.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/core/artifact-writer.ts`: added grouped artifact-path support so implementor results persist under story-specific artifact folders.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/core/prompt-assembly.ts`: added follow-up request support for retained-session continuation prompts.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/core/provider-adapters/shared.ts`: added shared subprocess execution, redaction, and strict provider-output parsing helpers.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/core/provider-adapters/index.ts`: added provider adapter factory/types.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/core/provider-adapters/codex.ts`: added Codex execution with explicit `exec resume` session handling and reasoning-effort override.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/core/provider-adapters/claude-code.ts`: added Claude Code execution with explicit `--resume` handling.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/core/provider-adapters/copilot.ts`: added the v1 scaffold that blocks retained-session continuation.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/tests/test-helpers.ts`: extended fixtures with run-config helpers, story fixtures, and fake provider executables in `PATH`.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/tests/story-implement-command.test.ts`: added red/green command coverage for launch, continuation fields, self-review pass count, auto-fixes, and surfaced uncertainty.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/tests/story-continue-command.test.ts`: added continuation coverage for explicit handles, follow-up files, and wrong-story rejection.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/tests/provider-adapter.test.ts`: added explicit-session resume coverage for Codex and Claude adapters.\\n- `processes/impl-cli/tests/result-contracts.test.ts`: added implementor result schema coverage and routing-status validation.\\n- tests: added 8 tests across `story-implement-command.test.ts` and `story-continue-command.test.ts`; modified 4 tests across `provider-adapter.test.ts` and `result-contracts.test.ts`; removed 0; total count after story 148; delta vs prior baseline 136 is `+12`\\n- gates run + result: Story 3 targeted test slice pass; `bun run typecheck` pass; `bun run capture:test-baseline --force` pass; `bun run green-verify` pass, including `build`, `validate`, repo-wide `bun test`, and `guard:no-test-changes`\\n- self-review findings fixed in this dispatch: none\\n- self-review findings surfaced to orchestrator: none\\n- open questions: none\\n- spec deviations: none\\n- recommended next step: accept Story 3 and move to Story 4, which should own the fresh verifier batch and quick-fix routing without expanding the retained implementor scope here\"}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
